text: This bench is surprisingly comfortable for a gas station rest stop...

Check out the old pay phone.

You walk into the phone booth and the phone starts to ring:
You dial your [color=red]home[/color] number into phone and it rings.
Thank goodness for picking up! I've got a [color=red]funny[/color] story to tell you.
What do you want to say to them:
Tell them that you are fine.
I'd really [color=red]like[/color] to hitch a ride back home with you.
I'm feeling [color=red]fine[/color] and have everything under control.
After telling them you are ok:
You leave, looking for something else.
There's that bench again! [p]Oh, a nap sounds [color=red]nice[/color] right now.
You go back to the bench and find a comfortable spot:
Hello? Who's there? Are you [color=red]looking[/color] for someone?
My name is Trinity. [p]What is your [color=red]name[/color]?
You pause for a second, suddenly unsure of yourself, with what seems like a basic question:
You [color=red]know[/color] the truth then. [p]The Matrix has you.
I'm here to get you out.
What you do next seems obvious, except:
I have something to do here.
The person on the other end of the phone hangs up.
Well, guess that's another [color=red]funny[/color] thing that happened to me today.
You put the old phone back on the hook and walk out of the phone booth, [color=red]lost[/color] in thought:
There are some [color=red]good[/color] vibes coming from this store.
Maybe someone will be [color=red]nice[/color] enough to help me get home.
Maybe the [color=red]person[/color] at the register can offer up some help.
You look at this [color=red]friendly[/color] person and ask for a ride home.
Yeah, I can [color=red]help[/color] you out, and maybe laugh about it later.
This place is [color=red]funny[/color], and not where I was when I fell asleep.
Ok brain, the pizza I ate last night was [color=red]wierd[/color], but how do get back to where I was?
You take your cell phone out of your pocket, and [color=green]laugh[/color] at the [color=red]cute[/color] cat picture on the lock screen.
Ok, what is the [color=red]right[/color] person who should I call that will make me feel happy?
That's where I [color=red]want[/color] to be, somewhere with funny people who will make me laugh.
